VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT @RawQuery|rawQuery\s*\(\s*[^,)]*\+
WHEN EXPR MISSING:SupportSQLiteQuery|SimpleSQLiteQuery|bindArgs
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects use of Room @RawQuery or rawQuery() with potential for unsanitized input.
TRACE Externalized mobile rule logic for RawQuery with User-Controlled Input.
